@startuml
title Cartographie du Pipeline : Ingestion vers Rendu (Extrusion Incluse)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam NoteBorderColor #A80036

package "CPU : Domaine Données" #LightBlue {
    [CSV Reader] as CSV
    [GeoJSON Reader] as GJSON
    [BaseNetwork] as BN
    [PreparedDataset] as PD
    [Country Geometry Generator] as CGG
}

package "CPU/GPU : Invariants & Précalcul" #LightGreen {
    [StaticTownPrecompute] as ST
    [Boundary N-Vectors] as NV
    [Dynamic Parameters] as DP
}

package "GPU : Passes de Calcul (Compute)" #LightCoral {
    [RawCone Kernel] as RCK
    [CiseledCone Kernel] as CCK
    [CurveGeometry Kernel] as CGK
}

package "Renderer : Babylon.js" #LightYellow {
    [Cone Mesh Adapter] as CMA
    [Country Mesh Adapter] as CMyA
    [Curve Mesh Adapter] as CurA
}

' Relations Données
CSV --> BN : assemble
GJSON --> BN : manifest
BN --> PD : prepare (SI units, rad)

' Focus GeoJSON & Extrusion
GJSON --> CGG : extract contours
note right of CGG
  **Logique d'Extrusion**
  1. Densification contour
  2. Delaunay (Points intérieurs)
  3. Duplication Z=hauteur
  4. Triangles murs latéraux
end note
CGG --> CMyA : Extruded Vertices [lon, lat, h]

' Flux Compute
PD --> ST : NED-to-ECEF Matrices
CGG --> ST : Point-in-Ring (City link)
CGG --> NV : Rad -> N-Vector [x,y,z,0]

' Execution GPU
ST --> RCK
DP --> RCK : RoadAlpha, year
RCK --> CCK : Raw Rims (ECEF)
NV --> CCK : Boundary Clipping Limits
CCK --> CMA : Ciseled Vertices (Projected)

PD --> CGK : Control Points [A,P,Q,B]
CGK --> CurA : Projected Samples

' Final Render
CMA --> [Babylon Scene]
CMyA --> [Babylon Scene]
CurA --> [Babylon Scene]

legend right
  | Couleur | Responsabilité |
  | <#LightBlue> | CPU / Métier |
  | <#LightGreen> | Partagé / Invariants |
  | <#LightCoral> | GPU / Parallèle |
  | <#LightYellow> | Affichage |
endlegend

@enduml
